com.jpm.test

Class SetUpData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jpm.test.SetUpData

  • public class SetUpData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class sets up static data in the memory to run the report. Please feel free to change and add more data to test. Be aware you may have to adjust the values of some final variables in the top of the SetUpDataTest class or it may fail some tests.
    Author:
    Lalit Mishra
